data.description: Explore this spacious five-bedroom home with a downstairs master suite featuring a large shower and walk-in closet. The open kitchen seamlessly connects to the dining and family rooms. A bonus room downstairs  adds flexibility, while the upstairs boasts a large media room and four secondary bedrooms. The front exterior showcases an appealing mix of brick, enhancing curb appeal. Call now to schedule a private tour.
